या फेरि प्रयास गर्नुहोस्।","This photo is already uploaded. Please upload a different one":"यो फोटो पहिले नै अपलोड गरिएको छ। कृपया अर्को अपलोड गर्नुहोस्।","This file cannot be uploaded because the file format is unsupported":"यो फाइल अपलोड गर्न सकिँदैन किनभने फाइल ढाँचा समर्थन गरिएको छैन।","This file cannot be uploaded because file size limit (100 MB) is exceeded":"यो फाइल अपलोड गर्न सकिँदैन किनभने फाइल साइज सीमा (१०० एमबी) नाघिएको छ","You've started writing a review. If you close this window, your text will be lost.":"तपाईंले समीक्षा लेख्न सुरु गर्नुभएको छ। यदि तपाईंले यो विन्डो बन्द गर्नुभयो भने, तपाईंको पाठ हराउनेछ।","Could you please copy your review and share it on other platforms? It only takes a moment and really helps us.":"के तपाईं आफ्नो समीक्षा प्रतिलिपि गरेर अन्य प्लेटफर्महरूमा साझा गर्न सक्नुहुन्छ? यसले थोरै समय लिन्छ र हामीलाई साँच्चै मद्दत गर्छ।",Posting:"पोष्ट गर्दै","Write Again":"फेरि लेख्नुहोस्","Write with AI":"AI सँग लेख्नुहोस्","Hang on, your review is being written…":"पर्खनुहोस्, तपाईंको समीक्षा लेखिँदैछ…","Share key points to generate a review":"समीक्षा बनाउन मुख्य बुँदाहरू साझा गर्नुहोस्","You've reached the limit of AI suggestions for now.":"तपाईंले अहिलेका लागि AI सुझावहरूको सीमा पुग्नुभएको छ।","See original ({{language}})":"मूल देख्नुहोस् ({{language}})","See translation ({{language}})":"अनुवाद हेर्नुहोस् ({{language}})"},sw:{reviews:"maoni","Based on":"Kulingana na","All Reviews":"Maoni Yote","Load More":"Pakia Zaidi","Owner Reply":"Jibu la Mmiliki","Read more":"Soma zaidi","View on":"Tazama kwenye","Overall Rating":"Ukadiriaji Jumla",on:"imewashwa","{{number}} reviews":"{{number}} hakiki","out of 5":"katika 5",Hide:"Ficha","Verified by {{supplierName}}":"Imethibitishwa na {{supplierName}}","Top Rated on {{supplierName}}":"Iliyopewa Alama Juu kwenye {{supplierName}}","Review us on {{supplierName}}":"Tupatie tathmini kwenye {{supplierName}}","AI-Generated Summary":"Muhtasari Uliotengenezwa na AI","Very Good":"Nzuri Sana",Good:"Nzuri","Post